title: Paper bags making machine US-ZD-QFJ08C[F]
title_uz: Qog'oz sumkalar (paket) ishlab chiqarish uskunasi US-ZD-QFJ08C[F]
title_ru: Машина для изготовления бумажных пакетов US-ZD-QFJ08C[F]
short_description: The following equipment US-ZD-QFJ08C[F] is used to produce paper bags. The manufactured products are mainly used for gifts and closable bags, that is, for taking food and fast food. The equipment produces 200 bags per minute, and with the additional function [F] it can produce up to 220 products per minute. The weight is about 15000 kg, the size is 11000*4400*1800 mm. The description also includes other models of this equipment. Their prices and parameters differ from each other.
short_description_uz: Quyidagi uskuna US-ZD-QFJ08C[F] qog'ozdan sumkalar ishlab chiqarishga xizmat qiladi. Ishlab chiqariluvchi mahsulotlar asosan sovg'alar uchun hamda og'zi nisbatan yopiladigan sumkalar, ya'ni taom va fast-food lar solish uchun xizmat qiladi. Uskuna daqiqasiga 200 ta paket ishlab chiqaradi, [F] qo'shimcha funksiyasi bilan esa daqiqasiga 220 tagacha mahsulot ishlab chiqaradi. Vazni taxminan 15000 kg, o'lchami 11000*4400*1800 mm dan iborat. Tavsifda bu uskunaning boshqa modellari ham o'rin olgan. Ularning narx va parametrlari bir-biridan farq qiladi.
